title: Delivery
alt: Ma'am, I admit that wasn't in the best taste, but you have to admire my delivery! Ha, ha get it? Oh god, don't throw those syringes! Your baby's fine!
transcript:
[In a delivery room.]
Doctor: There's the head... he's looking at me... Wait, he's crawling back into the womb.
Megan: What?!
Doctor: Yeah, it's the darnedest thing.
Megan: Um, what does it mean?
Doctor: My guess? Six more weeks of winter.
